<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What potential benefits can institutional investors expect from investing in Ethereum?</h3>



<p>Institutional investors who invest in Ethereum may benefit from potential long-term capital appreciation if the price of Ether (Ethereum&#8217;s native cryptocurrency) increases over time. They may also gain exposure to the growing blockchain industry and potentially earn passive income through staking or participating in decentralized finance (DeFi) protocols built on top of Ethereum&#8217;s network.</p>
